{"tid":1360482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商家佬、有錢佬，你有兩個選擇。","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:52:43.000Z","uid":167971,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"369ab2425bd30a06197d1c2d3c966bf065107446","tid":1360482,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"一係就幫<br />\n<br />\n一係就一齊死 <br />\n<br />\n解放軍一出 經濟就冧硬<br />\n到時就一鋪清袋 一切歸零<br />\n仲想喺屋企涼冷氣 訓晏覺 快活人生???<br />\n你準備跳樓都得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n窮人永遠比有錢人多<br />\n我錢就無架喇 又要捱貴租同物價<br />\n你地就唔同喇 依家咁舒服<br />\n萬一咩都冇晒 你哋頂唔頂得順呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身咩都無 唔差在無埋自由<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地最多一齊攬炒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼續做有錢佬定做窮人自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持解放軍入嚟!!!!!一齊共享大亞灣繁榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:窮人 唔知人生仲有咩意義"},{"pid":"dad428fe9796688a41dcbc03df290d4e642b4d57","tid":1360482,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"abc8a92db60cea79845dd3c2dc4eef930b775d9e","tid":1360482,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思!!<br />\n後日0726就係機場集會!!!<br />\n機場有無數外國旅客!!!<br />\n係對外發出香港嘅SOS求救訊號嘅大好機會!!!<br />\n一定要搞大佢!!!<br />\n宜家一齊推&darr;&darr;&darr;<br />\n<br />\n❲0726機場❳ 多國語言 發動全球文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[繼續開花] 到我地機師做野喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1